com.aliceapps.custompreferences.timePreference

Class CustomTimePreference

  • java.lang.Object
    • androidx.preference.Preference
      • androidx.preference.DialogPreference
        • com.aliceapps.custompreferences.timePreference.CustomTimePreference
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<androidx.preference.Preference>

    public class CustomTimePreference
extends androidx.preference.DialogPreference
    CustomTimePreference shows custom Time Picker dialog CustomTimePreference saves the time in the number of minutes since midnight How to use it in preferences.xml file:

    Preference layout has the same structure as ListPreference layout, must contain: TextView @android:id/title - will be used to show title TextView @android:id/summary - will be used to show summary

    Version:
    07.09.2020
    Author:
    alice.apps
